                            "description": "Smoothed Dirac delta delta_omega over the wetting run: near zero while the head is far from the transition, spiking to its peak 1/(pi*omega) = 318 m^-1 as h crosses zero, then decaying -- the switch firing in time.",
                            "x": {
                                "variable": "t",
                                "label": "time (s)"
