                            "description": "Smoothed Heaviside eta_omega at the fixed head h = 0.01 m as a function of the smoothing parameter omega (log x axis). Decreases monotonically from ~1 (sharp step, h >> omega) toward 0.5 (omega comparable to or larger than h).",
                            "x": {
                                "variable": "ω",
                                "label": "smoothing parameter omega (m)"
                            },
                            "y": {
                                "variable": "η_ω",
                                "label": "smoothed Heaviside eta_omega"
